beer.beer_description: Shenanigans took the idea of an icecream spider and brewed a spider-inspired beer based on a Milkshake IPA. A light malt base combined with some punchy hops for creaminess and berry character, vanilla and lactose, and a special flower for a bluey, purple haze. Now you're acting funny, but you don't know why... Brewed for GABS 2019.
